**Actor** | Town Power | Mini
__Basics__
The Actor is given the names of 2 townfolk roles, throughout the game they may use the powers of those two roles but only once each.
__Details__
At the very start of the game, the Actor is told the names of two townsfolk roles. They can use the powers of these roles but only once each. Targeting roles can only select a target one time. Roles that can't be used the first night or day have the same restrictions applied. It cannot copy roles that perform whispers. Passive powers have 1 use as well. You can use as many actions as the original role can in the span of 1 phase.
